[SHORT DESC]
A Ball used to catch Pokemon that causes the captured Pokemon to gain happiness faster.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>A Ball used to catch Pokemon. Has the same catch ratio as a Pok√© Ball. Will fail during Trainer battles. Cannot be used in Link or Wi-Fi battles.</p>

<p>Luxury Ball has a capture rate modifier of *1. If a Pokemon is captured in a Luxury Ball, it will gain an extra happiness value for each happiness raising event.</p>